            <h2>3. Opt-In and Consent</h2>
            <p>By providing your phone number and opting into our SMS notifications, you consent to receive recurring automated text messages (SMS, MMS) from us regarding service updates, offers, and other important notifications.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="one_line_col">
            <h2>4. Opt-Out Instructions</h2>
            <p>To stop receiving messages, reply “STOP,” “END,” “CANCEL,” “UNSUBSCRIBE,” or “QUIT” to any SMS message from us. You may also email us at support@chatsites.io with your opt-out request.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="one_line_col">
            <h2>5. Help and Support</h2>
            <p>If you are experiencing issues with our SMS notifications, you can reply with the keyword “HELP” to any message or email us at support@chatsites.io.</p>
          </div>
