            <h2>7. Privacy and Data Security</h2>
            <p>We value your privacy and do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="one_line_col">
            <h2>8. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected.</p>
          </div>
